snippet.title: What happened to My 600 lb life Amber Rachdi?
snippet.description: Amber Rachdi was a participant in the third season of the reality show "My 600 lb life."At only 23 years of age, she weighed  657 pounds by no means a normal. She had trouble walking more than a few feet, couldn’t drive as she barely fit in a car, She also had trouble taking a shower on her own. Fast forward now  Amber Rachdi has successfully turned around her life. More in the video. #My600lbLife #AmberRachdi #DrNowzaradan
